OL,3,CLimit jury trials to prevent 'total
OL,4,Csystem collapse' says court review
OL,6,FMore trials should take place without
OL,7,Fa jury to reduce the risk of "total
OL,8,Fcollapse" of the justice system in
OL,9,FEngland and Wales.
OL,11,FThat's according to former judge Sir
OL,12,FBrian Leveson, who was tasked by the
OL,13,Fgovernment to tackle the record-high
OL,14,Fcourt backlog in the two nations.
OL,16,FHe unveiled plans on Wednesday to
OL,17,Fshake up the structure of courts and
OL,18,Freclassify offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
