OL,6,FThe number of cases waiting to reach
OL,7,Fthe courtroom passed 75,000 for the
OL,8,Ffirst time in March, with some cases
OL,9,Fbeing listed for 2029.
OL,11,FSir Brian's recommendations have been
OL,12,Fmodelled to save approximately 9,000
OL,13,Fsitting days in the crown court each
OL,14,Fyear.
