OL,6,FOne of the main proposals is diverting
OL,7,Fcases to magistrates' courts, or to
OL,8,Fthe proposed Crown Court Bench
OL,9,FDivision, for trials to be heard by
OL,10,Fjudges.
OL,12,FJuries would be reserved to hear the
OL,13,Fmost serious cases, and defendants
OL,14,Fwould receive a 40% discount on their
OL,15,Fsentence if they plead guilty at the
OL,16,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,18,FThe review also proposed a greater use
OL,19,Fof cautions or unpaid work to move
OL,20,Fmore cases away from crown courtrooms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
