OL,3,CLimit jury trials to prevent 'total
OL,4,Csystem collapse' says court review
OL,6,FOffences with a maximum jail sentence
OL,7,Fof two years of less, such as drug
OL,8,Fpossession, bike theft and voyeurism,
OL,9,Fcould have sentences reduced to 12
OL,10,Fmonths imprisonment or less.
OL,12,FIn cases involving an assault on an
OL,13,Femergency worker, stalking and
OL,14,Fpossessing an indecent photograph of a
OL,15,Fchild, the defendant would no longer
OL,16,Fhave the right to choose a jury trial.
