OL,6,FA judge would decide whether a
OL,7,Fdefendant's case would be sent to the
OL,8,Fnew court or the Crown Court with a
OL,9,Fjury.
OL,11,FThe review report published on
OL,12,FWednesday is the first part of Sir
OL,13,FBrian's recommendations.
OL,15,FA second report focusing on court
OL,16,Fefficiency is expected to be published
OL,17,Flater in the year.
