OL,3,CLimit jury trials to prevent 'total
OL,4,Csystem collapse' says court review
OL,6,FThe former senior judge told reporters
OL,7,Fhe does not "rejoice" in the
OL,8,Frecommendations, but added: "I do
OL,9,Fbelieve that they are absolutely
OL,10,Fessential if we are to prevent our
OL,11,Fsystem from collapse."
OL,13,FSir Brian, chairman of the independent
OL,14,Freview of the criminal courts, said:
OL,15,F"It is well recognised that justice
OL,16,Fdelayed is justice denied, but the
OL,17,Frecord and rising court backlog means
OL,18,Fvictims, witnesses and defendants are
OL,19,Fwaiting months, sometimes years, for
OL,20,Fcases to come to trial - unable to
OL,21,Fmove on with their lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
