OL,6,F"This situation is simply
OL,7,Funacceptable."
OL,9,F"The reality of criminal courts which
OL,10,Fare no longer effective is already
OL,11,Fbeginning to materialise".
OL,13,FHe said the proposed reforms take a
OL,14,F"proportionate approach to trial
OL,15,Fprocesses while maintaining a right to
OL,16,Fa fair trial".
OL,18,F"These are not small tweaks but
OL,19,Ffundamental changes that will seek to
OL,20,Fmake the system fit for the 21st
OL,21,Fcentury."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
