OL,6,FThe Victims' Commissioner Baroness
OL,7,FNewlove warned that proposals like
OL,8,Fsentence discounts will "feel like
OL,9,Fjustice diluted once again" for
OL,10,Fvictims of crime, but added the
OL,11,Freforms were "necessary".
OL,13,F"There is no credible alternative, but
OL,14,Feven this may fall short of what's
OL,15,Ftruly needed," she said.
OL,17,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,18,Fministers will now consider the
OL,19,Frecommendations and will respond ahead
OL,20,Fof legislating changes in the autumn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
