OL,6,FResponding to the report, Law Society
OL,7,Ffor England and Wales president
OL,8,FRichard Atkinson said a new crown
OL,9,Fcourt division will not solve the
OL,10,Fbacklog on its own.
OL,12,F"Without sustained long-term
OL,13,Finvestment in the system dealing with
OL,14,Fboth demand on the courts and the
OL,15,Fcapacity of the courts, the Government
OL,16,Fwill simply be shifting the Crown
OL,17,FCourt backlog to the Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt backlog and creating another
OL,19,Fbacklog in the new division."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
