OL,6,FThe Magistrates' Association said
OL,7,Fmagistrates were "ready and willing"
OL,8,Fto support the changes, but more would
OL,9,Fbe needed to handle a new Criminal
OL,10,FCourt Bench Division.
OL,12,FThey proposed that the reforms would
OL,13,Frequire an additional 5,400
OL,14,Fmagistrates.
OL,16,FThe review comes as ministers accepted
OL,17,Fthe majority of recommendations to
OL,18,Fcurb long-term overcrowding in jails.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
